Webpage description (html):
Experience the essence of the Lake District with our 140ml Reed Diffuser Refill in Windermere. Extend the life of your Agnes and Cat Reed Diffuser in an environmentally friendly glass bottle with an aluminum cap.

These practical and long-lasting refills infuse the space for at least 3 months.

Imagine standing at the edge of Lake Windermere, where cool, crisp air mingles with the earthy scent of the countryside. This fragrance captures the essence of the serene Lake District, with hints of fresh greenery and the soothing stillness of the water.  

With our convenient refills, you can take a significant stride towards a more sustainable future and establish a space where your customers can always find their cherished scents.

Don't forget to add matching Agnes + Cat Reed Diffusers to your inventory!
